ze:10\n bar:Wawi\n  from: 21/05/2018 till: 24/02/2020 color:red text:\"[[Wan Azizah Wan Ismail]]\" fontsize:10\n \n</timeline>\n\n== Senior Ministers ==\nNo MP's has been appointed as the Deputy Prime Minister but the cabinet government under Prime Minister Tan Sri Muhyiddin Yassin has four senior ministers.\n\nThese four senior ministers are responsible for helping the Prime Minister coordinate Cabinet affairs on economics, security, development and education and social infrastructure.\n\nSenior ministers will also assist the Prime Minister in carrying out his duties as Prime Minister including chairing Cabinet meetings during Muhyiddin's absence.\n\nWith the presence of these senior ministers, there is currently no need for a Deputy Prime Minister to be appointed.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! No. \n!Portrait|| Name || Cluster || Party || Start of term || End of term\n|-\n| 1 \n|[[File:Azmin Ali 2019 (cropped).jpg|60px]]||[[Mohamed Azmin Ali]] (b.1964) || Economy || [[Malaysian United Indigenous Party|PPBM]] ||rowspan=\"4\"| 10 Mac 2020 ||rowspan=\"4\"| ''Incumbent''\n|-\n| 2 \n|[[File:DSIS3.jpg|60px]] ||[[Ismail Sabri Yaakob]] (b.1960) || Security || [[United Malays National Organisation|UMNO]]\n|-\n| 3 \n|[[File:Coat of arms of Malaysia.svg|60px]] ||[[Fadillah Yusof|Haji Fadillah Yusof]] (b.1962) || Infrastructure || [[Parti Pesaka Bumiputera Bersatu|PBB]]\n|-\n| 4 \n|[[File:Coat of arms of Malaysia.svg|60px]] || Dr. [[Mohd Radzi Md Jidin|Mohd. Radzi Md. Jidin]] (b.1977) || Education and Social || [[Malaysian United Indigenous Party|PPBM]]\n|}\n\n== Living former Deputy Prime Ministers ==\n<gallery class=\"centre\" caption=\"Living former Deputy Prime Ministers\">\n\nFile:Mahathir 2007.jpg|[[Mahathir Mohamad]]<br />served 1976\u20131981<br />born 1925 (age {{age|1925|7|10}})\nFile:Blank.jpg|[[Musa Hitam]]<br />served 1981\u20131986<br />born 1934 (age {{age|1934|4|18}})\nFile:Anwar Ibrahim.jpg|[[Anwar Ibrahim]]<br />served 1993\u20131998<br />born 1947 (age {{